data.description: Introducing a stunning 2-story home in Sequin, TX! This spacious property boasts 4 bedrooms and 3 baths, offering ample space for comfortable living. The highlight of this home is the oversized backyard, providing endless possibilities for outdoor activities and relaxation. Enjoy the privacy and tranquility of having no backdoor neighbors, creating a peaceful retreat. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity! **Owner Financing Available!**
